quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  61,10,"ya 'ayuha aladhin sddaqu allah warasulah waeamiluu bshreh, hal 'urshidkm 'iilaa tijaratan ezymt alshaan tunjikum min eadhab mwje?"
  61,11,"tdawmwn ealaa 'iimanikum biallah wrswlh, watujahidun fi sabil allh; lnsrt dinih bima tamlikun min al'amwal walanfs, dhlk khayr lakum min tijaratan aldnya, 'iin kuntum taelamun mdarr al'ashya' wmnafeha, famtthlu dhlk"
  61,12,"'in faealtum -ayha almwmnwn- ma 'amarakum allah bih ystr ealaykum dhnwbkm, wayudkhilakum janaat tajri min taht ashjarha alanhar, wamasakin tahrt zakiatan fi janaat 'iiqamat dayimat la tnqte, dhlk hu alfawz aldhy la fawz baedah. wanaemat 'ukhraa lkm- 'ayuha almwmnwn- tuhibuwnaha hi nasr min allah yatykm, wafath eajil yatimu ealaa aydykm. wbshshir almuminin -ayha alnby- bialnasr walfath fi aldnya, waljnt fi alakhrt"
  61,13,"'in faealtum -ayha almwmnwn- ma 'amarakum allah bih ystr ealaykum dhnwbkm, wayudkhilakum janaat tajri min taht ashjarha alanhar, wamasakin tahrt zakiatan fi janaat 'iiqamat dayimat la tnqte, dhlk hu alfawz aldhy la fawz baedah. wanaemat 'ukhraa lkm- 'ayuha almwmnwn- tuhibuwnaha hi nasr min allah yatykm, wafath eajil yatimu ealaa aydykm. wbshshir almuminin -ayha alnby- bialnasr walfath fi aldnya, waljnt fi alakhrt"
  61,14,"ya 'ayuha aladhin sddaqu allah warasulah waeamiluu bshreh, kunuu ansarana ldyn allh, kama kan asfya' eisaa ansarana ldyn allah hin qal lahum eysa: man yatawalaa minkum nsry w'ieanty fima yuqrrib 'iilaa allh? qalu: nahn 'ansar din allh, fahtdt taayifat min bani 'israyyl, wdllat tayft, fa'ayadna aladhin amanuu biallah wrswlh, wanasarnahum ealaa man eadahm min firaq alnsara, fa'asbahuu zahirin elyhm; wdhlk bbetht muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"